    v1 = (tmp * wp.exp(v2))
    v1 = v2
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.50 / v0 + 0.82)) / (wp.sin(tmp + 0.99) * tmp))
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.57)) - v2)
    tmp = (0.50 * ((tmp + 0.43 - v2 + 0.18) / (v2 + 0.86 / v0 + 0.69)))

    data[tid] = v0
